  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Europe. The aim of this observational study is to investigate the
      efficacy (e.g. glycemic control) and safety (e.g. hypoglycemic episodes) when adding
      repaglinide to a monotherapy of metformin in type 2 diabetic patients under normal clinical
      practice
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
